Package: dynamic-wallpaper-editor
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: dynamic-wallpaper-editor-doc
Description: Dynamic Wallpaper Editor for Gnome
 The GNOME desktop allows the wallpaper to change with time.
 .
 These dynamic wallpapers are XML files, and you don't want to write these files in a 
 text editor: Dynamic Wallpaper Editor is a little utility for the 
 creation or the edition of these XML wallpapers.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.

