Description: Dynamic Wallpaper Editor for Gnome (common documentation)
 These dynamic wallpapers are XML files, and you don't want to write these files in a 
 text editor: Dynamic Wallpaper Editor is a little utility for the 
 creation or the edition of these XML wallpapers.
 .
